# Security

- Never commit secrets, API keys, tokens, or credentials.
- Document env vars in `.env.example` with fake values only.
- Do not log sensitive user data or expose internal errors to end users.
- Do not disable auth, validation, lint, or tests to unblock work without explaining why.
- Do not assume production data is safe to modify.
